defaultClubs.description: We, the Association for Computing Machinery at UH Manoa (ACManoa/ACM), are the largest computer science student organization at the University of Hawaii at Manoa.
We are an open community of people who love to watch Japanese anime, read manga, have an interest in gaming, cosplay, Japanese culture, western comics/animation, or anything related.
